                            <div class="resource-content">
                                <h4><i data-feather="radio"></i>Warriors in the Garden - This American Life</h4>
                                <p>
                                    This episode of <i>This American Life</i> is by reporter Saidu Tejan-Thomas Jr. of podcast <i>Resistance</i>, who tells the story of three men who came together to protest the murder of George Floyd. They were unified, loud, and impressive, but over time these three friends end up in three very different places. This episode tells of the heat of protests, attempted murder, the many expected cases of police misconduct, and how the three men eventually decided to best combat police brutality.
                                </p>
